org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel

Class XWPFPictureData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ooxml.POIXMLDocumentPart
      • org.apache.poi.xwpf.usermodel.XWPFPictureData

  • public class XWPFPictureData
extends POIXMLDocumentPart
    Raw picture data, normally attached to a WordprocessingML Drawing. As a rule, pictures are stored in the /word/media/ part of a WordprocessingML package.(原始图片数据，通常附加到WordcastingML Drawing。通常，图片存储在WordcastingML包的/word/media/部分中。)
    Author:
    Philipp Epp

      • getData

        public byte[] getData()
        Gets the picture data as a byte array.

        Note, that this call might be expensive since all the picture data is copied into a temporary byte array. You can grab the picture data directly from the underlying package part as follows:
        InputStream is = getPackagePart().getInputStream();

        (以字节数组形式获取图片数据。请注意，此调用可能会很昂贵，因为所有图片数据都被复制到临时字节数组中。您可以直接从底层包部分抓取图片数据，如下所示：InputStream is = getPackagePart（）.getInputStream（）;)
        Returns:
        the Picture data.(图片数据。)

      • getFileName

        public java.lang.String getFileName()
        Returns the file name of the image, eg image7.jpg . The original filename isn't always available, but if it can be found it's likely to be in the CTDrawing(返回图像的文件名，例如image7.jpg。原始文件名并不总是可用，但如果可以找到它，它很可能在CTDrawing中)
